                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 399 create
                        action accept
                        description "0x0806/ARP/Others"
                        match frame-type ethernet_II
                            etype 0x806
                        exit
                    exit
                    entry 433 create

                        description "0x8809/Slow Protocols/Broadcast"

                            etype 0x8809
                        exit
                    exit

    qos
        network-queue "nqNetwork" create
            description "Network Egress Queue"
            queue 1 create
                rate 100 cir 20
                mbs 100
                cbs 20
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            queue 2 best-effort create
                rate 100 cir 50
                cbs 50
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            queue 3 expedite create
                rate 100 cir 30
                cbs 30
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            queue 9 multipoint create
                mbs 50
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            queue 11 multipoint best-effort create
                cbs 20
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            queue 12 multipoint best-effort create
                rate 100 cir 50
                cbs 50
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            queue 13 multipoint expedite create
                rate 100 cir 30
                cbs 30
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            fc be create
                multicast-queue 11
                queue 1
                egress-hsmda
                    queue 1
                exit
            exit
            fc ef create
                multicast-queue 12
                queue 2
                egress-hsmda
                    queue 6
                exit
            exit
            fc h2 create
                multicast-queue 13
                queue 3
                egress-hsmda
                    queue 5
                exit
            exit
        exit
        slope-policy "spDrop" create
            high-slope
                start-avg 80
                max-avg 95
                max-prob 10
                no shutdown
            exit
            low-slope
                start-avg 30
                max-avg 95
                max-prob 20
                no shutdown
            exit
        exit
    exit

            exit
            queue 3 expedite create
                rate 800000 cir 300000
                cbs 30000
                mbs 80000 kilobytes
                high-prio-only 10
            exit
            fc be create
                queue 1
            exit 
            fc ef create
                queue 2
            exit 
            fc h2 create
                queue 3
            exit 
        exit
        sap-egress 20300 create
            description "300M-For-egress"
            queue 1 create
                rate 449280
            exit
        exit
        sap-egress 20500 create
            description "500M-For-egress"
            queue 1 create
                rate 748800
            exit
        exit
        network 100 create
            description "NETWORK QoS POLICY Ingress classification,Egress remarking "
            ingress
                default-action fc be profile in
                dscp be fc be profile out
                dscp cs1 fc ef profile in
                dscp cs2 fc ef profile in
                dscp cs3 fc ef profile in
                dscp cs4 fc h2 profile in
                dscp cs5 fc ef profile in
                dscp nc1 fc h2 profile in
                dscp nc2 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 0 fc be profile out
                lsp-exp 1 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 2 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 3 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 4 fc h2 profile in
                lsp-exp 5 fc ef profile in
                lsp-exp 6 fc h2 profile in
                lsp-exp 7 fc ef profile in
            exit
            egress
                remarking
                fc ef
                    dscp-in-profile cs5
                    dscp-out-profile cs5
                exit
                fc h2
                    dscp-in-profile cs4
                    dscp-out-profile cs4
                exit
            exit
        exit
        network 200 create
            description "Network QoS policy ingress need mark "
            ingress
                default-action fc ef profile in
            exit
            egress
            exit
        exit
    exit
